<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to ATC Africa</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #1f1f1f;
        background-color: #f6f7f9;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid #e6e7eb;
      }

      .header {
        background-color: #4b0082;
        padding: 32px 28px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #ffffff;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #3e006e;
      }

      .header h1 {
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }

      .header p {
        font-size: 14px;
        opacity: 0.9;
        font-weight: 400;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 28px;
      }

      .welcome-message {
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      .welcome-message h2 {
        color: #1f1f1f;
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .welcome-message p {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }

      .features {
        background-color: #f7f8fc;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-left: 4px solid #4b0082;
      }

      .features h3 {
        color: #1f1f1f;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .feature-list {
        list-style: none;
      }

      .feature-list li {
        padding: 6px 0;
        color: #333;
        position: relative;
        padding-left: 20px;
      }

      .feature-list li:before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        top: 10px;
        width: 6px;
        height: 6px;
        background-color: #4b0082;
        border-radius: 50%;
      }

      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #4b0082;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin: 16px 0;
      }

      .cta-button:hover {
        background-color: #3e006e;
      }

      .footer {
        background-color: #fafbfc;
        padding: 24px 28px;
        text-align: center;
        border-top: 1px solid #eceef2;
      }

      .footer p {
        color: #566074;
        font-size: 12px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .social-links {
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      .social-links a {
        display: inline-block;
        margin: 0 8px;
        color: #4b0082;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .social-links a:hover {
        color: #3e006e;
      }

      .highlight {
        color: #4b0082;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .container {
          margin: 10px;
          border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .header,
        .content,
        .footer {
          padding: 20px;
        }

        .header h1 {
          font-size: 20px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to ATC Africa</h1>
        <p>Your gateway to Africa's tech community</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <div class="welcome-message">
          <h2>
            Hello 
            <span class="highlight"><%= firstName %> <%= lastName %></span>!
          </h2>
          <p>
            Welcome to the African Tech Community (ATC Africa) - where
            innovation meets opportunity! We're thrilled to have you join our
            growing network of tech enthusiasts, entrepreneurs, and innovators
            across Africa.
          </p>
          <p>
            Your account has been successfully created and you're now part of a
            community that's shaping the future of technology in Africa.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="features">
          <h3>üöÄ What you can do with your ATC Africa account:</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>Discover and attend amazing tech events across Africa</li>
            <li>Connect with fellow tech professionals and entrepreneurs</li>
            <li>Submit and manage your own tech events</li>
            <li>Apply to become a speaker at events</li>
            <li>Explore sponsorship opportunities</li>
            <li>Stay updated with the latest tech trends and news</li>
            <li>Access exclusive resources and networking opportunities</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center">
          <a href="<%= websiteUrl %>" class="cta-button">Explore ATC Africa</a>
        </div>

        <p
          style="
            text-align: center;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 20px;
          "
        >
          Ready to dive in? Visit our platform to start exploring events and
          connecting with the community!
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p><strong><%= companyName %></strong></p>
        <p>Connecting Africa's Tech Community</p>
        <p>üìç <a href="<%= websiteUrl %>"><%= websiteUrl %></a></p>
        <p>üìß <a href="mailto:<%= companyEmail %>"><%= companyEmail %></a></p>

        <div class="social-links">
          <a href="#">Twitter</a> | <a href="#">LinkedIn</a> |
          <a href="#">Facebook</a> |
          <a href="#">Instagram</a>
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #adb5bd">
          ¬© <%= currentYear %> <%= companyName %>. All rights reserved.<br />
          This email was sent to <%= email %>. If you have any questions, please
          contact us at <%= supportEmail %>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
